        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Sign changes: (+ to -), (- to +). Total of 2 changes, so 2 or 0 positive roots."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Solve $\\frac{x}{x-3} = \\frac{3}{x-3} + 4$.",
