        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Factor: $\\frac{(x-3)(x+3)}{(x+2)(x+3)}$. Hole at $x=-3$, V.A. at $x=-2$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "If $\\frac{7x+1}{(x-1)(x+1)} = \\frac{A}{x-1} + \\frac{B}{x+1}$, find $B$.",
